snippet.title: F.L.U.D.D. in Super Mario Odyssey [mod trailer]
snippet.description:
Super Mario Odyssey is now one step closer to perfection. With the addition of everyone's favorite companion F.L.U.D.D. now you can FLY, SPRINT and LAUNCH Mario in the world of SMO. If you enjoy the mod let me know down below. (also consider liking as it helps me know your general thoughts)

Details:
__Mod Link__
GameBanana(https://gamebanana.com/mods/421691)
__Features__
3 F.L.U.D.D. Nozzles (Hover, Rocket, Turbo)
Original models from SMS
Custom UI for modes/water

___Credits___
Nintendo - for these two amazing games
All the amazing people that worked on Starlight
@CraftyBoss925 - for the base project used
@AmethystSZS  - helped with fixing some crashes and testing

Here's some other links I guess:
-Discord: https://discord.gg/VGEk56Mk5j
-Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/justkant8
